description: This is the second part of the "Lego The Passion of the Christ." It covers the biblical story of Jesus' trial by Pilate, His death on the cross, and His resurrection. I made this old version back in 2015. Check out "The Messiah: A Brickfilm" or "The Passion: A Brickfilm" for a more current movie.
